00:04:01.700 --> 00:04:05.710
Does the bolt come back faster when the gun is in the air, or when the entire

00:04:05.730 --> 00:04:09.730
thing is under water? Before I show you the answer I need to apologise to you. If you look back at the pistols

00:04:09.750 --> 00:04:13.740
underwater video you can see that I just blew out the back side of the aquarium but the

00:04:13.760 --> 00:04:17.780
