00:04:17.800 --> 00:04:21.800
normal plate glass. On tempered glass if you just break the edge the entire pane will shatter

00:04:21.820 --> 00:04:25.810
so obviously I messed up the experiment. I apologise for that. So here you go.

00:04:25.830 --> 00:04:29.840
Look at the difference between air and water. Enjoy.

